{"tid":1325218,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暴力及執法傷亡賠償計劃","createTime":"2019-07-16T21:12:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T14:46:55.000Z","uid":254330,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a03dc7a4e8c4fd1cc184cef286ab95502327096d","tid":1325218,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T21:12:38.000Z","msg":"見連登冇乜人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n這項計劃目的是提供經濟援助給因暴力罪行或因執法人員使用武器執行職務﹐以致受傷的人士或這些人士的受養人(如受害人因傷死亡)。此計劃無須供款﹐申請人亦無須接受經濟狀況調查，賠償款項由公帑支付。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">details</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swd.gov.hk/doc/social-sec/CLEICL1107.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swd.gov.hk%2Fdoc%2Fsocial-sec%2FCLEICL1107.pdf&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSaHDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=e75d7c4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swd.gov.hk/doc/social-sec/CLEICL1107.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_pubsvc/page_socsecu/sub_criminalan/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Findex%2Fsite_pubsvc%2Fpage_socsecu%2Fsub_criminalan%2F&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSaHDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=d8c7118f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_pubsvc/page_socsecu/sub_criminalan/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.memehk.com/posts/因警察暴力對待而受傷市民%E3%80%80或可申請執法傷亡賠償\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fposts%2F%E5%9B%A0%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E5%B0%8D%E5%BE%85%E8%80%8C%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%25E3%2580%2580%E6%88%96%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%A1%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSaHDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=b3d02559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.memehk.com/posts/因警察暴力對待而受傷市民%E3%80%80或可申請執法傷亡賠償</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">application form</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swd.gov.hk/doc/soc